Description: Command line tool for transferring data with URL syntax
 curl is a command line tool for transferring data with URL syntax,
 supporting HTTP, HTTPS, FTP, FTPS, SCP, SFTP, TFTP, DICT, TELNET,
 LDAP or FILE.
